high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on the right.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle to the right of the egg on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the counter on the left.
Put the knife inside a pan on the counter in front of the toaster.
Pick up the pan with the knife inside from the counter.
Turn right, hang a right at the fridge and turn right at the wall to face the white table.
Put the pan with the knife on the right edge of the table near the stool.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a knife on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and move towards the kitchen counter space to the left of the oven.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is on the counter.
Turn to the right and walk up to the counter that is in front of you.
Place the knife in the pan that is sitting on the counter.
Pick up the pan with the knife.
Turn to the right, walk forward until you reach the door, then turn right and walk almost all the way up to the wall, turning right to face the side of the kitchen table.
Place the pan with the knife in it down on the kitchen table.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan with a knife in it to the kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn around, step forward, then turn right to face the kitchen counter.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle in the center of the counter.
Turn around, step forward then hang left and go to the kitchen counter with the toaster.
Place the knife upright inside the right center of the pan.
Pick up the pan with the knife in it.
Turn right, walk towards the door, then turn right and go to the kitchen table.
Place the pan with the knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife into a pan and move the pan from the counter to the kitchen table.
